en.go_lesson1_ex10_slide2_content:
# Which One to Use?

&&(and): When both are true
```go
if score >= 70 && bonus > 0 {
    // 70 points or more "and" has bonus
    fmt.Println("Pass!")
}
```

||(or): When either one is true
```go
if isHoliday || isWeekend {
    // Holiday "or" weekend
    fmt.Println("Day off!")
}
```

Remember:
- `&&` → "A and B" both needed
- `||` → "A or B" either one is OK

